26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20that%20attending%20Ganesh%20Puja%20is%20not%20a%20crime%20and%20judges%20and%20politicians%20often%20share%20dais.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20visited%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20Delhi%20residence%20for%20Ganesh%20Puja%20yesterday%20and%20received%20a%20warm%20welcome%20from%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20Kalpana%20Das.%20%26quot%3BJoined%20Ganesh%20Puja%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20CJI%2C%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20Ji.%20May%20Bhagwan%20Shri%20Ganesh%20bless%20us%20all%20with%20happiness%2C%20prosperity%20and%20wonderful%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20and%20shared%20a%20photograph%20showing%20him%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20his%20wife%20praying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Raut%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20a%20leader%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20said%20such%20meetings%20raise%20doubts.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20must%20recuse%20himself%20from%20a%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20tussle%20between%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20and%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20it%20is%20Ganpati%20festival.%20How%20many%20people's%20houses%20has%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20visited%20so%20far%3F%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20information.%20Ganesh%20festival%20is%20celebrated%20in%20many%20places%20in%20Delhi%2C%20but%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20went%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20house%2C%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20together%20performed%20the%20Aarti.%20Our%20knowledge%20of%20God%20is%20such%20that%20if%20the%20custodians%20of%20the%20Constitution%20meet%20political%20leaders%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20then%20people%20have%20doubts%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20should%20recuse%20himself%20from%20the%20case%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Brelations%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20head%20of%20the%20central%20government%20are%20%26quot%3Bopenly%20visible%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20there%20is%20a%20tradition%20that%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20party%20and%20the%20judge%20has%20or%20is%20seen%20to%20have%20any%20relation%20with%20it%2C%20then%20he%20dissociates%20himself%20from%20that%20case.%20So%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20Chandrachud%20sahab%20should%20dissociate%20himself%20from%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut's%20party%20colleague%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20too%2C%20put%20out%20a%20post%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice's%20home%20and%20pointed%20to%20the%20repeated%20adjournments%20in%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BOkay.%20After%20the%20festivities%20are%20over%20hopefully%20CJI%20will%20deem%20fit%20and%20be%20slightly%20freer%20to%20conclude%20the%20hearing%20on%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20blatant%20disregard%20of%20Article%2010%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Oh%20wait%2C%20elections%20round%20the%20corner%20anyway%2C%20it%20can%20be%20adjourned%20for%20another%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MP%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%20Jha%2C%20RJD%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20the%20independence%20of%20every%20institution%20is%20not%20just%20theoretical%2C%20but%20must%20be%20seen.%20%26quot%3BGanpati%20puja%20is%20a%20personal%20issue%2C%20but%20you%20are%20taking%20a%20camera.%20The%20message%20it%20sends%20is%20uncomfortable.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20are%20tall%20personalities.%20So%20what%20can%20we%20say%20if%20they%20agreed%20to%20put%20out%20these%20photographs%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Jha%20shared%20the%20visuals%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20with%20the%20caption%3A%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20state%20of%20the%20republic%20....ladies%20and%20gentlemen.%20Jai%20Hind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%20for%20their%20criticism%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit.%20%26quot%3BAttending%20Ganesh%20Pooja%20is%20no%20crime.%20On%20many%20occasions%2C%20judiciary%20and%20politicians%20share%20stage.%20On%20auspicious%20functions%2C%20marriages%2C%20programs%20-%20but%20if%20PM%20attends%20it%20at%20house%20of%20CJI%20%2C%20Uddhav%20Sena%20MP%20doubts%20integrity%20of%20CJI%20%26amp%3B%20SC.%20Congress%20ecosystem%20attacks%20SC%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20did%20in%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Poonawalla%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bshameful%20contempt%20of%20court%20%26amp%3B%20abusing%20judiciary%26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP%20leader%20also%20said%20a%202009%20Iftar%20party%20hosted%20by%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20attended%20by%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20KG%20Balakrishnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726127760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjtu40si8_pm-cji_625x300_12_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-opposition-vs-bjp-after-pm-visits-chief-justices-home-for-ganesh-puja-6547551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20massive%20political%20row%20has%20erupted%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20residence%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Ganesh%20Puja.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-opposition-vs-bjp-after-pm-visits-chief-justices-home-for-ganesh-puja-6547551%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20dead%20after%20400-year%20-old%20fort%20wall%20collapses%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%