ictions%20to%20retaliate%20against%20the%20West's%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20one%20issue%3A%20He%20still%20needs%20to%20fund%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20profits%20from%20oil%20exports%20are%20likely%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Putin%20told%20his%20government%20to%20consider%20the%20export%20of%20strategic%20commodities%2C%20such%20as%20uranium%2C%20nickel%2C%20and%20titanium%2C%20according%20to%20state%20news%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fpolitics%2F1841901%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETASS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20restricting%20supplies%20of%20a%20number%20of%20goods%20to%20us.%20Well%2C%20maybe%20we%20should%20also%20impose%20certain%20restrictions%3F%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20any%20such%20limits%20should%20only%20be%20imposed%20if%20they%20do%20not%20%26quot%3Bharm%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Putin%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20wasn't%20saying%20he%20was%20expecting%20action%20%26quot%3Btomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20a%20commodities%20giant%20and%20a%20top%20exporter%20of%20the%20three%20metals%20Putin%20highlighted%2C%20so%20any%20disruption%20to%20supply%20could%20have%20serious%20global%20fallout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20uses%2C%20uranium%20is%20used%20for%20nuclear%20energy%20generation%2C%20nickel%20is%20used%20in%20batteries%2C%20and%20titanium%20is%20used%20in%20aerospace%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20already%20banned%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhome.treasury.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fjy2249%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20metal%20imports%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fprohibiting-imports-of-uranium-products-from-the-russian-federation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euranium.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20took%20note%3A%20Three-month%20nickel%20on%20the%20London%20Metal%20Exchange%