0Alliance.%20The%20exact%20reason%2C%20however%2C%20can%20only%20be%20determined%20through%20a%20proper%20analysis%20of%20the%20captured%20animals%2C%20he%20told%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20one-off%20incident.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20regular%20occurrence.%20There%20must%20be%20a%20rabid%20animal%20or%20something%20similar%20that%20triggered%20this%20issue.%20Normally%2C%20this%20does%20not%20happen.%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20the%20first%20such%20incident%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20The%20forest%20department%20is%20conducting%20surveys%20to%20identify%20the%20problematic%20animal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%2C%20who%20has%20also%20headed%20Project%20Tiger%20and%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20said%20that%20rabies%20and%20canine%20distemper%20virus%20can%20sometimes%20alter%20the%20behaviour%20of%20big%20cats%2C%20making%20them%20lose%20their%20fear%20of%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20the%20cause.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20capture%20the%20animal%2C%20analyse%20the%20sample%2C%20and%20diagnose%20the%20issue%20properly%20to%20determine%20the%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20tigers%20occasionally%20become%20%26quot%3Bman-eaters%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20also%20is%20not%20a%20common%20occurrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHunting%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%20It%20is%20not%20easy.%20So%2C%20when%20they%20get%20older%20or%20are%20unable%20to%20hunt%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20they%20may%20target%20easy%20prey%20like%20cattle.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20their%20canines%20are%20broken%20or%20their%20paws%20injured%2C%20they%20may%20attack%20humans%20or%20livestock%20only%20when%20they%20are%20in%20distress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20tigers%20do%20not%20usually%20identify%20humans%20as%20prey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20tiger%20confuses%20people%20crouching%20in%20fields%20with%