anges%20to%20its%20technology%20group%2C%20comes%20as%20the%20firm%20faces%20a%20slowdown%20in%20demand%20for%20parts%20of%20its%20advisory%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPwC%20US%20leader%20Paul%20Griggs%20announced%20the%20restructuring%20and%20layoffs%20to%20staff%20in%20a%20memo%2C%20obtained%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fpwc-laying-off-1-800-employees-plans-restructuring-of-products-business-b5dfe7c1%3Fmod%3Dlatest_headlines%C2%A0%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20%E2%80%9Cpositioning%20our%20firm%20for%20the%20future%2C%20creating%20capacity%20to%20invest%2C%20and%20anticipating%20and%20reacting%20to%20the%20market%20opportunities%20of%20today%20and%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20announcement%2C%20made%20on%20September%2011%2C%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20sombre%20anniversary%20of%20the%20firm's%20loss%20of%20five%20colleagues%20in%20the%202001%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20development%20marks%20a%20significant%20shift%20for%20PwC%2C%20which%20had%20avoided%20layoffs%20in%20the%20US%20since%202009%2C%20unlike%20its%20peers%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20(EY)%2C%20Klynveld%20Peat%20Marwick%20Goerdeler%20(KPMG)%20and%20Deloitte.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20restructuring%20will%20see%20PwC's%20products%20and%20technology%20teams%20more%20deeply%20integrated%20into%20individual%20business%20lines.%20The%20changes%20come%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20structural%20overhaul%20initiated%20by%20Paul%20Griggs%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20US%20leader%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETim%20Grady%2C%20PwC's%20US%20chief%20operating%20officer%20(COO)%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20remain%20competitive%20and%20position%20our%20business%20for%20the%20future%2C%20we%20are%20continuing%20to%20transform%20areas%20of%20our%20firm%20and%20are%20aligning%20our%20workforce%20to%20better%20support%20our%20strategy%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20the%20WSJ%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20PwC's%20China%20office%20is%20also%20facing%20a%20crisis%20after%20losing%20a%20major%20client%2C%20Country%20Garden%20Holdings.%20This%20loss%20comes%20amid%20scrutiny%20over%20PwC's%20role%20in%20auditing%20China%20Evergrande%20Group%2C%20which%20is%20accused%20of%20a%20%2478%20billion%20fraud%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20PwC%20China%20has%20implemented%20cost-cutting%20measures%20and%20layoffs.%20Reuters%20reported%20on%20September%205%20that%20over%2050%20Chinese%20firms%2C%20including%20Bank%20of%20China%2C%20have%20dropped%20PwC%20as%20their%20auditor%20or%20scrapped%20plans%20to%20rehire%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECountry%20Garden%20cited%20PwC's%20failure%20to%20meet%20the%20deadline%20for%20publishing%20its%20audited%202023%20financial%20statements%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726123920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvcjo7f5o_job-generic-_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpwc-to-cut-1-800-us-jobs-in-first-major-layoffs-since-2009-6547009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PricewaterhouseCoopers%20(PwC)%20is%20set%20to%20lay%20off%20approximately%201%2C800%20employees%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20marking%20its%20first%20major%20round%20of%20layoffs%20since%202009.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpwc-to-cut-1-800-us-jobs-in-first-major-layoffs-since-2009-6547009%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drama%20at%20Israeli%20startup%2C%20new%20CEO%20announced%3B%20old%20says%20he%20will%20not%20leave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publi