%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-woman-stabbed-to-death-by-brother-in-law-she-had-affair-with-cops-6546871%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20'Net%20ID'%20To%20New%20Books%2C%20Xi's%20Ideological%20Grip%20On%20China%20Is%20Tightening%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc1d8v888_china_625x300_12_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Cyberspace%20Administration%20and%20its%20Ministry%20of%20Public%20Security%20have%20mooted%20an%20initiative%20to%20create%20internet%20identification%20for%20netizens%20in%20China.%20Plans%20are%20afoot%20to%20issue%20digital%20identification%20that%20will%20be%20used%20by%20netizens%20instead%20of%20their%20real%20identities%20when%20opening%20online%20profiles.%20The%20justification%20for%20this%20move%20is%20to%20safeguard%20users%20from%20sharing%20personal%20data%2C%20which%20may%20be%20retained%20by%20private%20digital%20platforms.%20While%20the%20authorities%20have%20maintained%20that%20applying%20for%20internet%20identification%20is%20voluntary%2C%20there%20is%20apprehension%20that%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20(CPC)%20will%20exercise%20greater%20oversight%20over%20the%20Net%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20point%20to%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20tightening%20his%20grip%20on%20civil%20society.%20The%20exercise%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20public%20life%20but%20seems%20to%20encompass%20the%20education%20sector%20and%20the%20military%20as%20well.%20The%20Party%20leadership%20met%20in%20mid-July%20for%20its%20yearly%20plenary%20session%2C%20which%20determined%20the%20direction%20of%20important%20policy%20initiatives.%20The%20resolution%20of%20the%20session%20announced%20plans%20to%20work%20on%20a%20unified%20national%20population%20management%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProject%20Of%20'National%20Rejuvenation'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20set%20of%20regulations%20was%20issued%20recently%20with%20respect%20to%20educational%20institutions%20that%20seek%20to%20improve%20the%20pool%20of%20educators.%20The%20main%20aim%20of%20the%20Party-state%20is%20to%20uplift%20the%20societal%20status%20of%20teachers%2C%20enhancing%20their%20skills%2C%20and%20paring%20down%20their%20workload.%20Xi%20wants%20teachers%20to%20not%20merely%20impart%20lessons%20but%20to%20incubate%20a%20high-quality%20workforce%20for%20his%20vision%20of%20a%20modern%20Chinese%20economy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20rules%20seek%20educators%20to%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20Party's%20line%20on%20ideological%20matters%2C%20and%20draw%20the%20line%20with%20respect%20to%20any%20violations.%20According%20to%20government%20statistics%2C%20China%20has%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20combine%20of%20teachers%2C%20totalling%20over%2018%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcomitantly%2C%20students%2C%20too%2C%20are%20in%20the%20Party's%20crosshairs.%20In%20what%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20education%20sector%2C%20China's%20political%20elite%20in%20its%20Politburo%20Standing%20Committee%20and%20officials%20across%20provinces%20attended%20Xi's%20address%20to%20mark%20Teachers'%20Day%20this%20month.%20While%20Xi%20made%20a%20pitch%20to%20expand%20academic%20exchanges%20overseas%20and%20research%20cooperation%20and%20sought%20a%20greater%20say%20in%20international%20education%20governance%2C%20he%20also%20underscored%20the%20need%20to%20impart%20more%20political%20training%20in%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20this%20ideological%20guidance%20would%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20project%20of%20'national%20rejuvenation'%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20build%20the%20nation's%20strength.%20There%20is%20also%20stress%20on%20fostering%20a%20'sense%20of%20community'%20for%20the%20Chinese%20nation%20through%20the%20use%20of%20the%20official%20script%20and%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtecting%20Future%20Generations%20From%20'Sabotage'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20article%20published%20in%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China's%20journal%2C%20%3Cem%3EQiushi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Xi%20raised%20the%20bogey%20of%20hostile%20forces%20in%20the%20West%20trying%20to%20subvert%20the%20Party's%20leadership%2C%20and%20plans%20of%20a%20'colour%20revolution'%20in%20China.%20He%20justifies%20the%20moves%20of%20the%20Party%20at%20exerting%20greater%20control%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20the%20future%20generation%20from%20sabotage%2C%20and%20create%20'socialist%20successors'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20state-run%20media%20builds%20on%20Xi's%20thesis%2C%20warning%20of%20efforts%20by%20intelligence%20agencies%20to%20specifically%20target%20young%20students%20for%20recruitment%20and%20infiltration%20through%20social%20media.%20In%20a%20damage-control%20mode%2C%20new%20textbooks%20have%20been%20issued%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20national%20security%20that%20seek%20to%20wean%20students%20away%20from%20pop%20culture's%20potential%20for%20instigating%20a%20'colour%20revolution'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ideological%20Oversight%20Over%20PLA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20realm%20of%20defence%2C%20Xi%2C%20as%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Central%20Military%20Commission%20(CMC)%2C%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20oversight%20of%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%2C%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20rectification%20in%20the%20services.%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20National%20Defence%20posted%20an%20article%20that%20credited%20Xi%20for%20tackling%20the%20challenge%20of%20%26quot%3Blax%20discipline%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20PLA%20ranks%20that%20endured%20during%20his%20predecessors'%20tenures.%20The%20commentary%20supported%20improved%20supervision%20mechanisms%2C%20citing%20Chairman%20Mao%20Zedong's%20Yan'an%20Rectification%20campaign.%20The%20ministry%20seeks%20better%20discipline%20within%20the%20ranks.%20The%20Yan'an%20campaign%20of%20the%201940s%20sought%20to%20improve%20the%20Party's%20ideological%20moorings%20with%20rank-and-file%20poring%20over%20Mao's%20speeches.%20Historians%20state%20that%20the%20rectification%20campaign's%20outcome%20was%20that%20cadres%20critical%20of%20Mao%20were%20on%20the%20Party's%20sidelines%2C%20with%20the%20Chairman%20strengthening%20his%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelying%20On%20'Faithfuls'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20has%20also%20come%20to%20light.%20Recently%2C%20two%20former%20defence%20ministers%20-%20Wei%20Fenghe%20and%20Li%20Shangfu%20-%20were%20expelled%20from%20the%20Party%20over%20accusations%20of%20bribery.%20In%20a%20conference%20of%20the%20military%20brass%20convened%20in%20June%2C%20incidentally%20in%20Yan'an%2C%20Xi%20stated%20his%20intent%20to%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20corrupt%20elements%20and%20terminate%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20corruption.%20He%20already%20supports%20scrutiny%20of%20departments%20engaged%20in%20defence-related%20manufacturing%20by%20anti-corruption%20officials%20to%20unearth%20corruption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20has%20underlined%20that%20the%20Party's%20strength%20lies%20in%20PLA's%20organisational%20accord%20and%20that%20the%20'gun'%20(meaning%20the%20army)%20ought%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20those%20faithful%20to%20the%20Party.%20In%20line%20with%20this%2C%20the%20PLA%20is%20increasingly%20being%20staffed%20by%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20reliable%26quot%3B%20personnel%20in%20the%20upper%20echelons.%20For%20example%2C%20He%20Hongjun%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20executive%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20Central%20Military%20Commission%20(CMC)%20Political%20Work%20Department%2C%20which%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20party-building%20and%20political%20education%20within%20the%20military%2C%20was%20named%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Flailing%20Economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20triggers%20for%20Xi%20calling%20for%20greater%20control%20citing%20the%20bogeyman%20of%20a%20colour%20revolution%20lie%20in%20conditions%20that%20have%20developed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20his%20own%20policies.%20Chinese%20policymakers%20targeted%20a%20GDP%20(Gross%20Domestic%20Product)%20growth%20of%20around%205%25%20this%20year%20but%20could%20achieve%20only%20up%20to%204.7%25%20in%20the%20April%20to%20June%20quarter.%20Factory%20output%20has%20stalled%20and%20the%20sale%20of%20new%20flats%20is%20at%20an%2018-year%20low.%20Unemployment%20remains%20high%3B%20the%20Party%20even%20stopped%20publishing%20the%20damaging%20statistics%20recently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20labour%20unrest%20in%20the%20form%20of%20strikes%20in%20factories%20increased%20in%20the%20January-June%20period%2C%20according%20to%20China's%20official%20data.%20Social%20unrest%20has%20caught%20the%20Party%20unawares%2C%20as%20also%20evidenced%20by%20the%20demonstrations%20that%20broke%20out%20across%20China%20in%20December%202022%20against%20COVID-19%20restrictions.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20protests%20against%20the%20Party%20took%20the%20form%20of%20many%20boycotting%20paying%20mortgages%20on%20property%20to%20financial%20institutions%20in%20light%20of%20the%20worsening%20economic%20situation%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic-induced%20curbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20conclude%2C%20as%20the%20economic%20situation%20worsens%20in%20China%2C%20Xi%20is%20tightening%20his%20grip%20on%20disparate%20sectors%20like%20military%2C%20education%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20interactions.%20Through%20greater%20social%20control%2C%20the%20Party%20seeks%20to%20protect%20itself%20from%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20whose%20political%20model%20forms%20the%20foundation%20for%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5