ncomfortable%20about%20a%20man%20who%20was%20inside%20the%20shop%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2020%20minutes%20after%20that%20text%2C%20she%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20floor%20covered%20in%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20recorded%20by%20Smith%20was%20key%20in%20convicting%20him%20of%20the%20horrific%20murder.%20In%20the%20clip%2C%20a%20man%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20gonna%20hurt%26quot%3B%20a%20woman%20and%20ordered%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bjust%20get%20down%20on%20the%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20can%20be%20heard%20screaming%20as%20the%20man%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20over%2C%20it's%20over%2C%20it's%20over%2C%20it's%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20stabbing%2C%20he%20fled%20the%20furniture%20store%20through%20the%20back%20door%20and%20left%20Ms%20Kupfer%20bleeding%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20Smith%20had%20planned%20to%20attack%20a%20woman%20who%20alone%20and%20left%20his%20house%20prepared%20to%20kill.%20Ms%20Kupfer's%20lawyer%20called%20him%20a%20Hannibal%20Lecter-style%20sicko%20who%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20slaughtering%20women%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20man%20hated%20women.%20It's%20easier%20probably%20to%20sleep%20at%20night%20to%20think%20something%20is%20wrong%20with%20him%20rather%20than%20face%20the%20truth%20that%20this%20man%20was%20on%20a%20crusade%20to%20hunt%2C%20to%20destroy%20and%20to%20kill%20for%20the%20mere%20fact%20that%20she%20was%20female%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20the%20police%20found%20an%20audio%20recorded%20and%20a%20filet%20knife%20(used%20to%20slice%20and%20prepare%20fish).%20The%20knife%20had%20bent%20after%20the%20frenzied%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20items%20were%20covered%20in%20his%20DNA%20which%20was%20key%20in%20proving%20his%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%2C%20who%20had%20a%20long%20crimi