22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%2023rd%20anniversary%20of%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%2C%20NASA%20released%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20only%20American%20astronaut%20in%20space%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Frank%20Culbertson%2C%20who%20was%20reflecting%20on%20witnessing%20the%20tragedy%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20dated%20September%2012%2C%202001%2C%20Culbertson%20recollects%20the%20moment%20he%20learned%20of%20the%20attacks%20while%20being%20aboard%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS).%20Describing%20his%20shock%20and%20horror%20upon%20hearing%20about%20the%20events%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20obviously%20the%20world%20changed%20today.%20What%20I%20say%20or%20do%20is%20very%20minor%20compared%20to%20the%20significance%20of%20what%20happened%20to%20our%20country%20today%20when%20it%20was%20attacked%20by....%20by%20whom%3F%20Terrorists%20is%20all%20we%20know%2C%20I%20guess.%20Hard%20to%20know%20at%20whom%20to%20direct%20our%20anger%20and%20fear...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECulbertson%2C%20who%20was%20serving%20as%20the%20commander%20of%20Expedition%20Three%20at%20that%20time%2C%20captured%20images%20of%20the%20smoke%20plume%20rising%20from%20lower%20Manhattan%20shortly%20after%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Twin%20Towers.%20His%20letter%20vividly%20narrates%20his%20experience%20of%20seeing%20his%20country%20under%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20terrorist%20attacks%20of%20all%20time%20that%20killed%203000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20describe%20how%20it%20feels%20to%20be%20the%20only%20American%20completely%20off%20the%20planet%20at%20a%20time%20such%20as%20this.%20The%20feeling%20that%20I%20should%20be%20there%20with%20all%20of%20you%2C%20dealing%20with%20this%2C%20helping%20in%20some%20way%2C%20is%20overwhelming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECulbertson%C2%A0witnessed%20the%20smoke%20rising%20from%20New%20York%20City%20as%20they%20passed%20overhead.%20He%20captured%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20smoke%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20having%20an%20%26quot%3Bodd%20bloom%26quot%3B%20at%20its%20base.%20He%20later%20learned%20that%20the%20pilot%20of%20the%20plane%20that%20hit%20the%20Pentagon%20was%20his%20classmate%2C%20Captain%20Charles%20Burlingame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%2023%20years%20after%20the%20attack%2C%20a%20memorial%20exists%20where%20the%20Twin%20Towers%20once%20stood%20to%20remember%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20terror%20attack.%20Pew%20Research%20in%20its%20study%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20think%20of%20an%20event%20that%20so%20profoundly%20transformed%20US%20public%20opinion%20across%20so%20many%20dimensions%20as%20the%209%2F11%20attacks.%26quot%3B%20Culbertson's%20photograph%20and%20his%20letter%20serve%20as%20a%20lasting%20record%20of%20that%20fateful%20day%20in%20American%20history%2C%20noting%20that%20things%20would%20%26quot%3Bnever%20be%20the%20same%20again%26quot%3B%20after%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726111500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F16kqsnu_nasa-911-_625x300_12_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-9-11-attacks-looked-like-from-space-nasa-shares-haunting-image-6545898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%2023rd%20anniversary%20of%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%2C%20NASA%20has%20released%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20only%20American%20astronaut%20in%20space%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Frank%20Culbertson%2C%20who%20was%20reflecting%20on%20witnessing%20the%20tragedy%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-9-11-attacks-looked-like-from-space-nasa-shares-haunting-image-6545898%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ame