apability%20of%20the%20UltraPlus%20isn't%20just%20for%20sucking%20up%20your%20finished%20pile%20of%20leaves%20after%20you're%20done%20blowing.%20It%20also%20comes%20in%20handy%20for%20properties%20that%20have%20landscaping%20features%20like%20bushes%2C%20fences%2C%20or%20boulders.%20Leaves%20tend%20to%20get%20trapped%20against%20these%20obstacles%2C%20and%20regular%20blowers%20can%20have%20trouble%20getting%20them%20out.%20By%20switching%20the%20machine%20to%20vacuum%20mode%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20walk%20around%20and%20suck%20up%20these%20troublemakers%2C%20then%20get%20back%20to%20blowing%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20you'll%20have%20to%20physically%20remove%20the%20narrow%20blower%20tube%20and%20attach%20the%20wider%20vacuum%20tube%20when%20switching%20functions.%20This%20is%20a%20fairly%20simple%20process%2C%20though.%20A%20convenient%20zippered%20vacuum%20bag%20keeps%20your%20mulched%20debris%20contained%20until%20you're%20ready%20to%20dispose%20of%20it%2C%20eliminating%20that%20awkward%20step%20of%20scooping%20a%20leaf%20pile%20into%20a%20trash%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20characteristics%20of%20the%20Toro%2051621%20UltraPlus%20is%20how%20environmentally%20friendly%20it%20is.%20Its%20corded%20power%20source%20results%20in%20fewer%20emissions%20than%20gas%20machines.%20Also%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20mulched%20leaves%20as%20fertilizer%20for%20your%20garden%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsustainability.wustl.edu%2Frethinking-lawn-equipment-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20lawn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20budget%20for%20a%20high-end%20machine%2C%20the%20low-priced%20Toro%20PowerJet%20F700%20delivers%20an%20impressive%20amount%20of%20power%20in%20a%20small%20package.%20Yahoodain%20recommended%20this%20model%2C%20citing%20it