20volume%20and%20runs%20a%20little%20louder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Quietist%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuietist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENoise%20pollution%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20reasons%20leaf%20blowers%20are%20facing%20bans%20or%20restrictions%20in%20some%20communities.%20Gas%20powered%20blowers%20can%20crank%20up%20to%20100%20decibels%3B%20louder%20than%20a%20subway%20train.%20The%20Ryobi%20Whisper%20Series%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20name%20with%20the%20lowest%20decibel%20output%20we've%20found%20in%20a%20leaf%20blower.%20Its%2057%20decibel%20output%20is%20about%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20running%20refrigerator%2C%20and%20less%20than%20a%20standard%20vacuum%20cleaner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20its%20quiet%20operation%2C%20the%20Roybi%20Whisper%20Series%20is%20an%20all-around%20excellent%20performer.%20Its%20cordless%20operation%20allows%20for%20free%20movement%2C%20and%20it%20weighs%20just%20under%2010%20pounds%2C%20so%20nearly%20anyone%20can%20handle%20it.%20With%20the%20speed%20tip%20attached%2C%20it's%20capable%20of%20blowing%20190%20miles%20per%20hour%2C%20making%20quick%20(and%20quiet)%20work%20of%20cleaning%20up%20your%20yard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20its%20battery%20operated%2C%20we%20recommend%20this%20blower%20for%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20yards.%20You'll%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20clearing%20significant%20acreage%20on%20just%20one%20charge%20(though%20it%20does%20come%20with%20a%20backup%20battery).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fryobi-whisper-series-leaf-blower-review%5C%22%3ERyobi%20Whisper%20Series%20Leaf%20Blower%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20battery-powered%5C%22%3EBest%20battery-powered%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20maximum%20power%20and%20portability%2C%20the%20Ego%20Power%2B%20LB6504%20could%20be%20the%20perfect%20fit.%20This%20cordless%20electric%20blower%20should%20be%20able%20to%20easily%20power%20through%20most%20residential%20chores.%20Should%20you%20encounter%20any%20heavy%2C%20wet%2C%20or%20unruly%20debris%2C%20you%20can%20hit%20the%20turbo%20button%20for%20a%20temporary%20boost%20of%20air.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20variable%20speed%20trigger%20of%20the%20Ego%20LB6504%20also%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20dial%20in%20the%20precise%20level%20of%20power%20you're%20looking%20for%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20the%20cruise-control%20button%2C%20you%20can%20lock%20in%20that%20speed%20for%20as%20long%20as%20you%20like.%20This%20feature%20would%20be%20really%20handy%20for%20tasks%20that%20require%20minimal%20power%20when%20you%20don't%20feel%20like%20maintaining%20trigger%20pressure%20the%20whole%20time.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20appreciate%20the%20flat%20bottom%20design%20of%20this%20blower%2C%20which%20keeps%20it%20from%20rolling%20over.%20By%20reducing%20the%20chances%20of%20it%20tipping%20over%20and%20getting%20scratched%20or%20chipped%2C%20it%20can%20extend%20the%20lifespan%20of%20the%20machine.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20you%20are%20limited%20by%20the%20running%20time%20of%20any%20battery-powered%20blower%2C%20the%20Ego's%20powerful%205.0Ah%2056%20V%20lithium%20battery%20provides%20roughly%2075%20minutes%20of%20running%20time%20per%20charge.%20That%20should%20be%20enough%20time%20for%20most%20lawns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brushless%20motor%20of%20the%20Ego%20LB6504%20is%20another%20valuable%20feature.%20I%20recommend%20always%20going%20with%20brushless%20tools%20if%20you%20have%20the%20choice.%20Considering%20how%20much%20value%20they%20add%20in%20terms%20of%20efficiency%20and%20increased%20lifespan%2C%20it%20can%20be%20worth%20the%20extra%20upfront%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEgo%20is%20one%20of%20the%20more%20varied%20outdoor%20tool%20brands%20out%20there%20right%20now%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20thinking%20of%20starting%20a%20collection%2C%20they're%20a%20great%20brand%20to%20go%20with.%20Once%20you%20have%20more%20than%20one%2C%20you%20can%20mix%20and%20match%20batteries%20and%20cut%20down%20on%20time%20spent%20waiting%20for%20them%20to%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impressive%20power%20and%20run%20time%20of%20the%20Ego%20LB6504%20make%20it%20relatively%20heavy.%20If%20you're%20fine%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20extra%20pounds%2C%20this%20blower%20is%20a%20great%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20backpack%5C%22%3EBest%20backpack%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20Husqvarna%20150BT%20Gas%20Backpack%20Leaf%20Blower%20is%20considered%20a%20mid-size%20commercial%20model%20in%20terms%20of%20power%2C%20its%20smaller%20size%20and%20lower%20price%20point%20make%20it%20ideal%20for%20residential%20use.%20If%20you%20don't%20need%20gale-force%20power%20but%20still%20want%20the%20portability%20and%20comfort%20needed%20to%20clear%20large%20yards%20and%20fields%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20choice.%20Dedrick%20highly%20recommends%20this%20model%20for%20homeowners%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20their%20products%20that%20I%20have%20used%20are%20borderline%20professional%20grade%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20priced%20affordably%20and%20they%20last.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Husqvarna%20150BT%20weighs%20much%20more%20than%20a%20handheld%20blower%20but%20is%20still%20relatively%20lightweight%20for%20a%20backpack%20model.%20Its%20shoulder%20harness%20distributes%20the%20unit's%20weight%20evenly%20across%20the%20shoulders%2C%20and%20I%20found%20its%20sturdy%2C%20balanced%20feel%20to%20be%20more%20comfortable%20than%20expected.%20When%20testing%2C%20this%20secure%20fit%20also%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20accomplish%20other%20yard%20work%20tasks%20that%20require%20two%20hands%2C%20like%20clearing%20branches%20out%20of%20the%20way%2C%20moving%20around%20trash%20cans%2C%20or%20climbing%20up%20a%20ladder.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20the%20ergonomic%20joystick%20of%20the%20Husqvarna%20150BT%20to%20be%20comfortable%20to%20use%20and%20simple%20to%20understand.%20Plus%2C%20the%20cruise%20control%20setting%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20lock%20in%20whatever%20setting%20I%20liked%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20throttle%20adjuster.%20In%20addition%20to%20meeting%20California's%20emissions%20standards%2C%20the%202.15%20horsepower%20X-Torq%20engine%20reduces%20fuel%20consumption%20by%2020%25%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20roam%20longer%20before%20needing%20to%20refuel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssembling%20the%20Husqvarna%20150BT%20out%20of%20the%20box%20took%20only%20a%20few%20minutes.%20Since%20it%20included%20the%20necessary%20wrench%2C%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20go%20hunting%20through%20my%20toolbox.%20Starting%20it%20up%20was%20a%20breeze%20too.%20After%20filling%20the%20fuel%20tank%2C%20I%20followed%20the%20instructions%20printed%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20and%20it%20fired%20up%20after%20a%20couple%20pulls%20of%20the%20handle.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Husqvarna%20150BT%20is%20still%20the%20loudest%20option%20on%20our%20list%2C%20though%20not%20by%20much.%20To%20protect%20yourself%20from%20potential%20hearing%20damage%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20purchase%20ear%20protection%20to%20wear%20while%20operating%20the%20blower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%24330%20price%20tag%20is%20fairly%20high%2C%20but%20considering%20Husqvarna's%20reputation%20for%20quality%20and%20performance%2C%20not%20entirely%20unreasonable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20light-duty%5C%22%3EBest%20light-duty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPowered%20by%20a%2024-volt%20ion%20battery%2C%20the%20Greenworks%202400702%2024V%20Leaf%20Blower%20is%20a%20great%20option%20for%20those%20who%20may%20not%20need%20the%20raw%20power%20of%20gas-powered%20or%20corded%20models%20and%20want%20the%20freedom%20to%20roam%20without%20worrying%20about%20wrangling%20extension%20cords.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapable%20of%20generating%20330%20CFM%2C%20the%20Greenworks%202400702%20is%20great%20for%20smaller%20maintenance%20jobs%20like%20clearing%20leaves%20from%20your%20patio%2C%20air%20drying%20a%20newly%20washed%20car%2C%20or%20blasting%20grass%20clippings%20off%20the%20driveway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20use.%20There's%20no%20power%20button%20to%20switch%20it%20on%3B%20you%20simply%20squeeze%20the%20trigger%20to%20activate%20it.%20Even%20though%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20power%20of%20other%20blowers%2C%20I%20preferred%20the%20Greenworks%20for%20quick%2C%20light-duty%20jobs%2C%20simply%20because%20of%20its%20hassle-free%20startup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeighing%20about%20as%20much%20as%20a%202-liter%20soda%20bottle%2C%20the%20Greenworks%20requires%20minimal%20effort%20to%20maneuver.%20The%20variable%20speed%20trigger%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20adjust%20the%20air%20speed.%20My%20biggest%20takeaway%20from%20using%20this%20blower%20is%20how%20little%20effort%20it%20takes%20to%20operate%20and%20how%20much%20I%20appreciated%20not%20being%20a%20sweaty%20mess%20after%20using%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20drawback%20to%20the%20Greenworks%202400702%20is%20its%20relatively%20short%20runtime.%20A%20fully%20charged%20battery%20will%20last%20about%2010%20minutes%2C%20so%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20suitable%20for%20larger%20properties.%20You%20can%20use%20their%20batteries%20as%20backups%20if%20you%20own%20other%20Greenworks%20power%20tools%20since%20they're%20all%20universal.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenworks%20is%20a%20great%20brand%20for%20tools%20in%20general.%20They're%20consistently%20a%20very%20popular%20choice%20with%20homeowners%20and%20offer%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20products%20to%20choose%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20leaf%20blower%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaf%20blowers%20can%20vary%20in%20quite%20a%20few%20ways%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20you're%20familiar%20with%20the%20available%20options%20before%20making%20a%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20which%20type%20of%20leaf%20blower%20is%20best%20for%20you%3A%20handheld%20or%20backpack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHandheld%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20are%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20leaf%20blowers%2C%20and%20have%20a%20top-mounted%20handle%20for%20comfortable%20one-handed%20use.%20Their%20light%20weight%20and%20compact%20size%20is%20convenient%20to%20store%2C%20and%20since%20handheld%20blowers%20are%20typically%20less%20powerful%20than%20backpack%20models%2C%20are%20best%20for%20smaller%20yards%20and%20quick%20tasks.%20Some%20handheld%20blowers%20offer%20extra%20features%20like%20vacuum%20capability%2C%20mulchers%2C%20and%20leaf%20bags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackpack%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20heavy-duty%20machines%20generate%20a%20ton%20of%20power%2C%20and%20are%20strapped%20to%20the%20user's%20back%20with%20a%20shoulder%20harness.%20This%20distributes%20their%20weight%20evenly%20across%20the%20shoulders%2C%20making%20them%20comfortable%20to%20use%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time.%20Their%20trigger%20throttle%20provides%20precise%20control%2C%20but%20their%20long%20nozzles%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20maneuver%20and%20aim%20into%20awkward%20positions.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20large%20property%2C%20or%20heavy%2C%20wet%20debris%20to%20clean%20up%2C%20you%20need%20a%20backpack%20blower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20Source%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaf%20blowers%20are%20either%20gas-powered%20or%20electric%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20their%20pros%20and%20cons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGas%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGas-powered%20leaf%20blowers%20are%20the%20most%20powerful%2C%20and%20commonly%20used%20by%20commercial%20landscaping%20crews.%20For%20large%20properties%20that%20require%20a%20long%20running%20time%20and%20unlimited%20range%2C%20or%20properties%20that%20lack%20available%20power%20outlets%2C%20gas-powered%20models%20are%20the%20most%20effective%20solution.%20Their%20noisy%20combustion%20engines%20generate%20harmful%20fumes%20though%2C%20requiring%20messy%20fuel%20mixes%20and%20maintenance%20tasks%20not%20found%20on%20electric%20models.%C2%A0Yahoodain%20suggested%20that%20most%20homeowners%20should%20probably%20only%20opt%20for%20a%20gas-powered%20blower%20if%20they%20need%20to%20blow%20areas%20over%201%2F4%20acre.%20Dedrick%20adds%20that%20%26quot%3Bhandheld%20gas-powered%20leaf%20blowers%20are%20heavy%2C%20and%20the%20vibration%20they%20create%20makes%20them%20difficult%20to%20use%20for%20extended%20periods%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectric%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECorded%20leaf%20blowers%20that%20plug%20into%20your%20home's%20electrical%20socket%20are%20simple%20to%20use%20and%20have%20an%20unlimited%20runtime%2C%20although%20their%20portability%20is%20limited%20by%20the%20length%20of%20your%20extension%20cord.%20Battery-powered%20blowers%20combine%20the%20easy%20operation%20of%20corded%20blowers%20with%20the%20portability%20of%20gas%2C%20but%20their%20batteries%20create%20their%20own%20issues.%20Dedrick%20explains%20that%20when%20you%20go%20with%20a%20battery-powered%20tool%2C%20their%20batteries%20won't%20be%20interchangeable%20between%20brands.%20This%20means%20that%20you'll%20probably%20want%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20same%20tool%20brand%2C%20to%20avoid%20any%20battery%20incompatibility%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%20level%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you'd%20prefer%20to%20keep%20the%20noise%20level%20to%20a%20minimum%2C%20consider%20going%20with%20an%20electric%20blower%20over%20gas-powered.%20Most%20brands%20also%20advertise%20their%20max%20decibel%20level%20(dBA)%2C%20which%20you%20can%20then%20use%20to%20compare%20potential%20blowers%20and%20make%20sure%20you%20choose%20the%20quietest%20option.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20blower%20you%20choose%2C%20you%20should%20always%20wear%20ear%20protection%20when%20operating%20it.%20Even%20if%20it's%20a%20quieter%20model%2C%20hearing%20damage%20is%20cumulative%2C%20and%20adds%20up%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20what%20features%20would%20be%20most%20helpful%20to%20you%20and%20your%20blowing%20tasks.%20Some%20blowers%20convert%20to%20a%20vacuum%20and%20include%20cloth%20leaf%20bags%2C%20so%20you%20can%20suck%20up%20leaf%20piles%20without%20bending%20over.%20Others%20have%20impellers%20that%20mulch%20up%20leaves%20as%20they%20travel%20through%20the%20nozzle%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20fit%20much%20more%20in%20the%20bag%20before%20emptying.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20regulations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20can%20legally%20operate%20your%20leaf%20blower%20in%20your%20area.%20Regulations%20and%20outright%20bans%20against%20gas-powered%20blowers%20are%20passing%20across%20the%20country%2C%20so%20consult%20your%20local%20officials%20before%20purchasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20leaf%20blowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20in%20fall%20attire%20walks%20along%20a%20sidewalk%20holding%20the%20Ryobi%20Leaf%20Blower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65205af19f7ca8b2bbdc61ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you're%20worried%20about%20noise%20pollution%2C%20the%20Ryobi%20Whisper%20Series%20Leaf%20Blower%20is%20the%20quietest%20leaf%20blower%20we've%20tested.%3Cp%3EColleen%20Sullivan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20as%20a%20landscaper%20at%20a%20large%20state%20park%2C%20a%20job%20that%20required%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20leaf-blower%20work%20with%20a%20range%20of%20types%20and%20brands.%20In%20addition%20to%20my%20experience%2C%20I%20sourced%20and%20tested%20several%20popular%20leaf%20blowers%20when%20considering%20options%20for%20this%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20local%20expert%20for%20advice%20and%20insight.%20Nick%20Yahoodain%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abclosangeles.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdvanced%20Builders%20and%20Contractors%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20extensive%20experience%20using%20leaf%20blowers%20in%20his%20business.%20Douglas%20Dedrick%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnaturallandscapedesigns.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENatural%20Landscape%20Designs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20landscaper%20with%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20experience.%20I%20used%20all%20this%20testing%2C%20research%2C%20and%20experience%20to%20put%20together%20several%20criteria%20to%20evaluate%20and%20compare%20potential%20blowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20all%20this%20testing%2C%20research%2C%20and%20experience%20to%20put%20together%20several%20criteria%20to%20evaluate%20and%20compare%20potential%20blowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%20level%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20serious%20health%20issues%20associated%20with%20prolonged%20exposure%20to%20loud%20noises%2C%20it's%20also%20annoying%20and%20uncomfortable.%20I%20sourced%20and%20compared%20the%20dB(A)%20level%20of%20each%20machine%20and%20made%20sure%20to%20exclude%20any%20models%20that%20were%20substantially%20noisier%20than%20others%20without%20any%20clear%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20effective%20leaf%20blower%20should%20be%20straightforward%20and%20convenient%20to%20start%2C%20operate%2C%20and%20control.%20I%20paid%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20layout%20and%20design%20of%20the%20controls%2C%20including%20power%20boost%20and%20cruise%20control%20features%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shape%20and%20design%20of%20the%20carrying%20handle.%20I%20also%20researched%20user%20reviews%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20weren't%20frequent%20complaints%20about%20the%20unit%20being%20complicated%20or%20frustrating%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20an%20extra%20pound%20or%20two%20can%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20how%20comfortable%20your%20blower%20is%20to%20operate.%20If%20blower%20models%20in%20the%20same%20category%20were%20a%20fairly%20close%20match-up%20in%20terms%20of%20power%20and%20usability%2C%20I%20tended%20to%20choose%20the%20lighter%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20top%20picks%20compared%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriteria%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EToro%2051621%20UltraPlus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EToro%2051624%20PowerJet%20F700%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ERyobi%20Whisper%20Series%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreenworks%202400702%2024V%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EEgo%20Power%2B%20LB6504%20Cordless%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EHusqvarna%20150BT%20Gas%20Backpack%20Blower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E68%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E70%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E57%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E65%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E65%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E72%20dB(A)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%20(1%20easy%20to%203%20more%20difficult)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E3%20(short%20run%20time)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E2%20(heavier%20than%20other%20blowers)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E3%20(more%20difficult%20to%20maneuver)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E8.9%20pounds%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E6.6%20pounds%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E9.7%20pounds%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4.4%20pounds%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E12.9%20pounds%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E22.5%20pounds%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQ%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaf%20blower%20FAQ%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20I%20need%20a%20cordless%20leaf%20blower%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20batteries%20have%20become%20more%20powerful%20and%20less%20bulky%2C%20cordless%20electric%20leaf%20blowers%20have%20become%20more%20commonplace.%20These%20machines%20are%20much%20easier%20to%20maintain%20than%20their%20gas-powered%20competitors%20and%20don't%20directly%20produce%20emissions.%20They%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20shorter%20runtime%2C%20however%2C%20making%20them%20less%20than%20ideal%20for%20large-scale%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20corded%20and%20battery-powered%20blowers%20have%20the%20advantage%20of%20running%20silent%20when%20in%20idle%20mode%2C%20unlike%20gas-powered%20machines%20that%20are%20still%20fairly%20loud%20when%20idling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20CFM%20and%20MPH%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECFM%20(cubic%20feet%20per%20minute)%20measures%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20air%20that%20passes%20through%20the%20nozzle%20of%20the%20leaf%20blower%20in%20one%20minute.%20%26quot%3BThe%20higher%20the%20CFM%2C%20the%20more%20air%20the%20blower%20will%20output%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20clear%20a%20wider%20area%20in%20less%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yahoodain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiles%20per%20hour%20(MPH)%20refers%20to%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20air%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20blower.%20Yahoodain%20explains%20that%20you%20can%20maximize%20this%20speed%20by%20using%20different%20sizes%20and%20shapes%20of%20nozzles.%20An%20open%2C%20circular%20nozzle%20allows%20more%20air%20to%20come%20out%20at%20once%2C%20while%20a%20wider%2C%20tapered%20nozzle%20will%20give%20you%20more%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20use%20a%20leaf%20blower%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20just%20wander%20out%20into%20the%20yard%20and%20start%20blowing%2C%20you're%20probably%20going%20to%20waste%20time%20and%20energy.%20Having%20a%20strategy%20in%20place%20ensures%20that%20you're%20working%20efficiently%20and%20won't%20waste%20time%20covering%20the%20same%20areas%20over%20and%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20avoid%20doubling%20up%20on%20work%20areas%2C%20you%20need%20to%20designate%20a%20collection%20point%20for%20your%20leaves%20or%20debris.%20This%20is%20typically%20the%20center%20of%20the%20yard%2C%20preferably%20on%20a%20large%20tarp.%20If%20your%20work%20area%20is%20really%20big%2C%20separate%20it%20into%20sections%2C%20each%20with%20its%20own%20collection%20point.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeginning%20at%20the%20perimeter%2C%20use%20your%20blower%20to%20push%20the%20leaves%20towards%20the%20center%20of%20the%20yard%20in%20broad%20strokes%2C%20working%20your%20way%20around%20the%20yard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUse%20low%20shallow%20strokes%20and%20adjust%20the%20power%20of%20the%20blower%20as%20you%20get%20closer%20to%20the%20center.%20Don't%20stress%20over%20every%20single%20leaf.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnce%20your%20leaves%20and%20debris%20are%20collected%2C%20use%20the%20tarp%20to%20funnel%20them%20into%20a%20yard%20waste%20bag%20or%20use%20them%20in%20a%20compost%20pile.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20loud%20are%20leaf%20blowers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELeaf%20blowers%20are%20notoriously%20loud%20machines%20and%20can%20generate%20enough%20noise%20to%20cause%20significant%20hearing%20loss%20over%20time.%20It's%20possible%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Fhearing_loss%2Fwhat_noises_cause_hearing_loss.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edamage%20your%20hearing%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20leaf%20blower%20with%20a%20noise%20rating%20of%2080%20decibels%20and%20above%20for%20two%20hours%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20operating%20a%20leaf%20blower%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20wear%20ear%20protection.%20Two%20of%20our%20picks%2C%20the%C2%A0Husqvarna%20350BT%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0Worx%20WG520%20Turbine%2C%C2%A0are%20over%2080%20dB(A)%2C%20so%20take%20that%20into%20consideration%20when%20choosing%20your%20blower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20leaf%20blowers%20bad%20for%20the%20environment%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20blowers%2C%20both%20corded%20and%20battery-powered%2C%20don't%20directly%20generate%20emissions%2C%20as%20gas-powered%20models%20do.%20If%20an%20electric%20blower%20can%20meet%20your%20needs%2C%20there's%20no%20need%20to%20choose%20a%20gas-powered%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20lessen%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20your%20gas-powered%20blower%2C%20always%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20rated%20as%20CARB-compliant.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww2.arb.ca.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Air%20Resources%20Board%3C%2Fa%3E%20regulates%20outdoor%20landscaping%20emissions%20and%20rates%20equipment%20as%20CARB-compliant%20only%20if%20their%20emissions%20fall%20below%20a%20certain%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20gas-powered%20leaf%20blowers%20restricted%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20set%20on%20purchasing%20a%20gas-powered%20blower%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20check%20for%20any%20restrictions%20or%20regulations%20in%20your%20area.%20Hundreds%20of%20cities%20across%20the%20country%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhdsupplysolutions.com%2Fs%2Fleaf_blower_noise_regulation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20passed%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%20limiting%20the%20use%20of%20gas-powered%20leaf%20blowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20has%20taken%20the%20strictest%20stances%20against%20them%2C%20with%2016%20cities%20that%20have%20banned%20gas-powered%20blowers%20altogether.%20According%20to%20CARB%2C%20some%20cities%20have%20even%20introduced%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww2.arb.ca.gov%2Four-work%2Fprograms%2Fzero-emission-landscaping-equipment%2Fzero-emission-landscaping-equipment-incentive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade-in%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20incentivize%20people%20to%20switch%20to%20electric%20lawn%20care%20equipment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20of%20Columbia%20instituted%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20gas-powered%20leaf%20blowers%20on%20January%201%2C%202022.%20The%20nationwide%20push%20towards%20all-electric%20lawn%20equipment%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20be%20slowing%20down%20anytime%20soon%2C%20so%20even%20if%20you're%20not%20in%20an%20area%20affected%20today%2C%20that%20may%20change%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Toro%2051621%20UltraPlus%20Leaf%20Blower%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20safety%20glasses%20using%20the%20Toro%2051621%20to%20blow%20leaves%20off%20of%20a%20sidewalk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e7e61a22ff8391e561ff011%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Toro%2051621%20UltraPlus%20Leaf%20Blower%20is%20simple%20to%20use%2C%20and%20loaded%20with%20extra%20features.%3Cp%3EHome%20Depot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECorded%20electricity%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E8.9%20pounds%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20volume%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E350%20CFM%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20speed%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E250%20MPH%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%20level%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E68%20dB(A)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOversized%20handle%20allows%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20grip%20positions%2C%20built-in%20cord%20lock%2C%20storage%20bag%20for%20accessories%20and%20attachments%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERelatively%20loud%2C%20wet%20leaves%20can%20clog%20the%20machine%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20more%20bells%20and%20whistles%20a%20product%20advertises%2C%20the%20less%20effective%20its%20primary%20function%20ends%20up%20being.%20Luckily%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Toro%2051621%20UltraPlus%20leaf%20blower.%20Even%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20powerful%20vacuum%20and%20mulcher%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20lightweight%20blower%20capable%20of%20generating%20impressive%20air%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UltraPlus's%20powerful%20vacuum%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20it's%20my%20top%20pick.%20It%20features%20a%2012-amp%20motor%20that%20can%20suck%20in%20leaves%20and%20debris%20at%20an%20impressive%20410%20CFM.%20A%20heavy-duty%20metal%20impeller%20reduces%20them%20by%2088%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMetal%20impeller%20blades%20will%20stay%20sharper%20longer%20than%20plastic%20and%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20chip%20and%20crack.%20This%20durability%20puts%20less%20stress%20on%20the%20motor%2C%20maximizing%20efficiency%20and%20extending%20the%20lifespan%20of%20the%20blower%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Toro%2051621%20UltraPlus%20produces%20about%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20noise%20as%20a%20vacuum%20cleaner%2C%20a%20feature%20that%20your%20neighbors%20are%20sure%20to%20appreciate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vacuum%20capability%20of%20the%20UltraPlus%20isn't%20just%20for%20sucking%20up%20your%20finished%20pile%20of%20leaves%20after%20you're%20done%20blowing.%20It%20also%20comes%20in%20handy%20for%20properties%20that%20have%20landscaping%20features%20like%20bushes%2C%20fences%2C%20or%20boulders.%20Leaves%20tend%20to%20get%20trapped%20against%20these%20obstacles%2C%20and%20regular%20blowers%20can%20have%20trouble%20getting%20them%20out.%20By%20switching%20the%20machine%20to%20vacuum%20mode%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20walk%20around%20and%20suck%20up%20these%20troublemakers%2C%20then%20get%20back%20to%20blowing%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20you'll%20have%20to%20physically%20remove%20the%20narrow%20blower%20tube%20and%20attach%20the%20wider%20vacuum%20tube%20when%20switching%20functions.%20This%20is%20a%20fairly%20simple%20process%2C%20though.%20A%20convenient%20zippered%20vacuum%20bag%20keeps%20your%20mulched%20debris%20contained%20until%20you're%20ready%20to%20dispose%20of%20it%2C%20eliminating%20that%20awkward%20step%20of%20scooping%20a%20leaf%20pile%20into%20a%20trash%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20characteristics%20of%20the%20Toro%2051621%20UltraPlus%20is%20how%20environmentally%20friendly%20it%20is.%20Its%20corded%20power%20source%20results%20in%20fewer%20emissions%20than%20gas%20machines.%20Also%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20mulched%20leaves%20as%20fertilizer%20for%20your%20garden%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsustainability.wustl.edu%2Frethinking-lawn-equipment-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20lawn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3A%20Toro%2051624%20PowerJet%20F700%20Handheld%20Leaf%20Blower%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20using%20the%20Toro%2051624%20to%20blow%20leaves%20off%20a%20sidewalk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F617958ae38046100183ee03a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20the%20affordable%20price%20tag%2C%20the%20Toro%2051624%20PowerJet%20F700%20Handheld%20Leaf%20Blower%20still%20provides%20an%20impressive%20amount%20of%20power.%3Cp%3EToro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECorded%20electricity%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E6.6%20pounds%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20volume%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E725%20CFM%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20speed%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E140%20MPH%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E70%20dB(A)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPowerful%20output%2C%20lightweight%2C%20very%20affordable%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExtension%20cord%20must%20be%20purchased%20separately%2C%20not%20ideal%20for%20large%20properties%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20budget%20for%20a%20high-end%20machine%2C%20the%20low-priced%20Toro%20PowerJet%20F700%20delivers%20an%20impressive%20amount%20of%20power%20in%20a%20small%20package.%20Yahoodain%20recommended%20this%20model%2C%20citing%20its%20750%20CFM%20airflow%2C%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20on%20the%20market.%20It's%20perfect%20for%20large%20piles%20of%20wet%2C%20heavy%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lightweight%20design%20of%20the%20PowerJet%20makes%20it%20comfortable%20to%20use%20one-handed.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20adjustment%20dial%20to%20customize%20the%20power%20setting%20for%20use%20around%20delicate%20landscaping.%20The%20wide%20range%20of%20power%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20what%20makes%20it%20such%20a%20popular%20and%20effective%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compact%20size%20of%20the%20F700%20also%20makes%20it%20convenient%20to%20store%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20A%20handy%20little%20keyhole%20cut-out%20on%20the%20bottom%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20hang%20up%20on%20a%20nail%20or%20hook%20in%20your%20garage%20or%20tool%20shed.%20This%20makes%20the%20Toro%20ideal%20for%20users%20who%20don't%20have%20room%20for%20larger%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20impressive%20power%20and%20unlimited%20runtime%20of%20the%20Toro%20PowerJet%20F700%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20portability.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20if%20you're%20working%20in%20a%20relatively%20small%20area%20and%20need%20extra%20power%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20