ts%20relatively%20short%20runtime.%20A%20fully%20charged%20battery%20will%20last%20about%2010%20minutes%2C%20so%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20suitable%20for%20larger%20properties.%20You%20can%20use%20their%20batteries%20as%20backups%20if%20you%20own%20other%20Greenworks%20power%20tools%20since%20they're%20all%20universal.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenworks%20is%20a%20great%20brand%20for%20tools%20in%20general.%20They're%20consistently%20a%20very%20popular%20choice%20with%20homeowners%20and%20offer%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20products%20to%20choose%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20leaf%20blower%3Cp%3ELeaf%20blowers%20can%20vary%20in%20quite%20a%20few%20ways%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20you're%20familiar%20with%20the%20available%20options%20before%20making%20a%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20which%20type%20of%20leaf%20blower%20is%20best%20for%20you%3A%20handheld%20or%20backpack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHandheld%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20are%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20leaf%20blowers%2C%20and%20have%20a%20top-mounted%20handle%20for%20comfortable%20one-handed%20use.%20Their%20light%20weight%20and%20compact%20size%20is%20convenient%20to%20store%2C%20and%20since%20handheld%20blowers%20are%20typically%20less%20powerful%20than%20backpack%20models%2C%20are%20best%20for%20smaller%20yards%20and%20quick%20tasks.%20Some%20handheld%20blowers%20offer%20extra%20features%20like%20vacuum%20capability%2C%20mulchers%2C%20and%20leaf%20bags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackpack%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20heavy-duty%20machines%20generate%20a%20ton%20of%20power%2C%20and%20are%20strapped%20to%20the%20user's%20back%20with%20a%20shoulder%20harness.%20This%20distributes%20their%20weight%20evenly%20across%20the%20shoulders%2C%20making%20them%20comfortable%20to%20use%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time.%20Their%20trigger%20throttle%20provides%20precise%20control%2C%20but%20their%20long%20nozzles%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20maneuver%20and%20aim%20into%20awkward%20positions.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20large%20property%2C%20or%20heavy%2C%20wet%20debris%20to%20clean%20up%2C%20you%20need%20a%20backpack%20blower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20Source%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaf%20blowers%20are%20either%20gas-powered%20or%20electric%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20their%20pros%20and%20cons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGas%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGas-powered%20leaf%20blowers%20are%20the%20most%20powerful%2C%20and%20commonly%20used%20by%20commercial%20landscaping%20crews.%20For%20large%20properties%20that%20require%20a%20long%20running%20time%20and%20unlimited%20range%2C%20or%20properties%20that%20lack%20available%20power%20outlets%2C%20gas-powered%20models%20are%20the%20most%20effective%20solution.%20Their%20noisy%20combustion%20engines%20generate%20harmful%20fumes%20though%2C%20requiring%20messy%20fuel%20mixes%20and%20maintenance%20tasks%20not%20found%20on%20electric%20models.%C2%A0Yahoodain%20suggested%20that%20most%20homeowners%20should%20probably%20only%20opt%20for%20a%20gas-powered%20blower%20if%20they%20need%20to%20blow%20areas%20over%201%2F4%20acre.%20Dedrick%20adds%20that%20%26quot%3Bhandheld%20gas-powered%20leaf%20blowers%20are%20heavy%2C%20and%20the%20vibration%20they%20create%20makes%20them%20difficult%20to%20use%20for%20extended%20periods%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectric%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECorded%20leaf%20blowers%20that%20plug%20into%20your%20home's%20electrical%20socket%20are%20simple%20to%20use%20and%20have%20an%20unlimited%20runtime%2C%20although%20their%20portability%20is%20limited%20by%20the%20length%20of%20your%20extension%20cord.%20Battery-powered%20blowers%20combine%20the%20easy%20operation%20of%20corded%20blowers%20with%20the%20portability%20of%20gas%2C%20but%20their%20batteries%20create%20their%20own%20issues.%20Dedrick%20explains%20that%20when%20you%20go%20with%20a%20battery-powered%20tool%2C%20their%20batteries%20won't%20be%20interchangeable%20between%20brands.%20This%20means%20that%20you'll%20probably%20want%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20same%20tool%20brand%2C%20to%20avoid%20any%20battery%20incompatibility%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%20level%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you'd%20prefer%20to%20keep%20the%20noise%20level%20to%20a%20minimum%2C%20consider%20going%20with%20an%20electric%20blower%20over%20gas-powered.%20Most%20brands%20also%20advertise%20their%20max%20decibel%20level%20(dBA)%2C%20which%20you%20can%20then%20use%20to%20compare%20potential%20blowers%20and%20make%20sure%20you%20choose%20the%20quietest%20option.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20blower%20you%20choose%2C%20you%20should%20always%20wear%20ear%20protection%20when%20operating%20it.%20Even%20if%20it's%20a%20quieter%20model%2C%20hearing%20damage%20is%20cumulative%2C%20and%20adds%20up%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20what%20features%20would%20be%20most%20helpful%20to%20you%20and%20your%20blowing%20tasks.%20Some%20blowers%20convert%20to%20a%20vacuum%20and%20include%20cloth%20leaf%20bags%2C%20so%20you%20can%20suck%20up%20leaf%20piles%20without%20bending%20over.%20Others%20have%20impellers%20that%20mulch%20up%20leaves%20as%20they%20travel%20through%20the%20nozzle%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20fit%20much%20more%20in%20the%20bag%20before%20emptying.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20regulations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20can%20legally%20operate%20your%20leaf%20blower%20in%20your%20area.%20Regulations%20and%20outright%20bans%20against%20gas-powered%20blowers%20are%20passing%20across%20the%20country%2C%20so%20consult%20your%20local%20officials%20before%20purchasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20leaf%20blowers%3Cfigure