o%20Reshma%2C%20the%20team%20at%20Tocco%20ensures%20that%20all%20products%20are%20homemade%2C%20carefully%20crafted%20in%20small%20batches%2C%20and%20preservative-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20become%20a%20chef%20at%20Tocco%2C%20one%20must%20apply%20on%20the%20website.%20After%20an%20initial%20call%2C%20the%20top%20three%20dishes%20of%20the%20chef%20are%20discussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dishes%20must%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349127%2Fwoman-startup-bakery-cakelicious-cake-tubs-in-kolkata-fatema-barodawala-single-mother-business-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%2C%20preservative%20free%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20at%20least%2030%20days.%20They%20should%20be%20regional%20or%20local%20specialities.%20We%20ask%20them%20for%20an%20ingredient%20list%20and%20take%20the%20next%20steps%20based%20on%20that.%20No%20palm%20oil%20is%20allowed.%20Chefs%20send%20samples%20of%20their%20dishes%2C%20which%20a%20focus%20group%20tastes.%20We%20suggest%20changes%2C%20and%20if%20satisfied%2C%20we%20begin%20the%20onboarding%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reshma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tips%20to%20start%20a%20business%20from%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-17