ge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20does%20the%20ARAI%20certification%20mean%20for%20Plugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%3F%20This%20certification%20for%20the%20Chennai-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20fast%20charger%20and%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20signifies%20their%20compliance%20with%20stringent%20operational%20safety%20standards%20and%20efficiency%20norms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307090%2Fchennai-startup-builds-homegrown-iot-enabled-smart-ev-chargers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0back%20in%20December%202022%2C%20co-founder%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20majority%20of%20EV%20chargers%20in%20India%20today%20are%20being%20imported%20and%20are%20of%20low%20quality.%20They%E2%80%99re%20largely%20imported%20from%20China.%20%5BThis%20is%20because%5D%20Chinese%20chargers%20are%20priced%20low%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20support%20from%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20once%20installed%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plugzmart's%2060kW%20Fast%20Charger%20on%20the%20Left%3B%20Representational%20Image%20of%20a%20car%20charging%20on%20the%20Right%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe