0for%20representational%20purposes%20only%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20suicide%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20Rahul%20(name%20changed)%20received%20the%20most%20devastating%20message%20of%20his%20life%20%E2%80%94%20his%20girlfriend%20had%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend%20her%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20as%20quickly%20as%20he%20could%2C%20while%20praying%20that%20she%20would%20survive.%20His%20mind%20raced%20through%20their%20past%20conversations%2C%20trying%20to%20understand%20what%20could%20have%20driven%20her%20to%20such%20a%20desperate%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20his%20relief%2C%20she%20survived%2C%20and%20Rahul%20dedicated%20himself%20to%20helping%20her%20heal.%20As%20he%20nursed%20her%20back%20to%20health%2C%20he%20urged%20her%20to%20seek%20professional%20help%2C%20which%20she%20did%20a%20few%20days%20later%20by%20visiting%20a%20psychiatrist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20therapy%20and%20treatment%2C%20they%20discovered%20that%20her%20attempt%20had%20been%20an%20impulsive%20decision%2C%20made%20during%20a%20moment%20of%20overwhelming%20despair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trauma%20stemmed%20from%20a%20rough%20childhood%20where%20her%20father%20abandoned%20the%20family%2C%20leaving%20her%20home%20an%20unsafe%20and%20unstable%20environment.%20This%20deep-seated%20pain%20triggered%20an%20impulsive%20decision%20to%20get%20over%20the%20conflict%20by%20ending%20her%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20shocked%20Rahul%20and%20her%20loved%20ones%20the%20most%20was%20how%20she%20seemed%20completely%20fine%20to%20the%20outside%20world.%20She%20was%20a%20driven%20career%20woman%2C%20but%20no%20one%20knew%20the%20silent%20battles%20she%20was%2