ent%2C%20and%20supportive%20of%20loved%20ones%20who%20may%20be%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20to%20do%20if%20someone%20contemplating%20suicide%20comes%20to%20you%20for%20help%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CListening%20is%20the%20most%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priyanka%20Varma%2C%20a%20psychologist%20at%20The%20Thought%20Company%20and%20consultant%20at%20Holy%20Family%20Hospital%20in%20Mumbai.%20With%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%2C%20she%20specialises%20in%20working%20with%20young%20adults%20as%20they%20navigate%20a%20world%20beyond%20social%20media.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20how%20to%20support%20someone%20with%20suicidal%20thoughts%20is%20critical%2C%20so%20we%20spoke%20with%20Priyanka%20to%20learn%20what%20steps%20we%20can%20take%20to%20help%20those%20who%20may%20be%20struggling%20with%20suicidal%20tendencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20aware%20of%20the%20warning%20signs%20in%20someone%20contemplating%20such%20an%20ex